title: Sanissimo Bio
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, International, Italian, Organic, Western, Delivery, Take-out
description: Vegetarian restaurant using local ingredients. Offers many vegan takes on food such as lasagna, burgers, pasta, salads, desserts, smoothies. Has a fixed price daily lunch menu. Place is small with modern decor. Also is a small store selling healthy staples such as quinoa, amaranth, nut butters, quinoa pasta. Delivery takes one hour.
